{"id":1190,"date":"2021-02-16T21:51:35","date_gmt":"2021-02-16T16:21:35","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost?page_id=1190"},"modified":"2023-11-06T23:22:26","modified_gmt":"2023-11-06T17:52:26","slug":"sk","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/?page_id=1190","title":{"rendered":"Sketch"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-100 has-custom-font-size is-style-outline has-small-font-size\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-foreground-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">Homepage<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">For my sketches I use various tools to bring my drawings to life. When it comes to pencils, I have a range of options. The HB pencil is great for general sketching, while the 2B pencil provides darker lines and shading. For lighter lines, I use the 2H pencil. When I want to add depth and texture, I turn to charcoal pencils, such as the soft charcoal for rich blacks and the hard charcoal for finer details. To correct mistakes, I rely on kneaded erasers that can be shaped and molded. For smudging and blending, I use tortillons or blending stumps. Finaly, I scan them at highest resolution, and correct any distortion or bad colors using photoshop. All the images here are downscaled to less than 1000-pixel height and width, to not slow down the site. Finer details might not be visible.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"797\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2360\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-300x239.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-150x120.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-768x612.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-500x399.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/1-800x638.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Equal and opposite, an abstract sketch that randomly came up to me, made without any reference, just out of my mind.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"689\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2361\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-300x207.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-150x103.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-768x529.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-500x345.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/2-800x551.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Anarchy and a kid with a gun.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"669\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2362\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-300x201.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-150x100.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-768x514.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-500x335.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/3-800x535.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Chester Bennington back in 2017, at the end.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"774\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2363\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-300x232.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-150x116.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-768x594.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-500x387.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/4-800x619.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">People close to me.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"716\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2364\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-300x215.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-150x107.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-768x550.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-500x358.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/5-800x573.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Bear Grylls back when I was a fan.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"873\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2365\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-300x262.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-150x131.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-768x670.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-500x437.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/6-800x698.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Benedict Cumberbatch from Sherlock Holmes.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"763\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2366\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-300x229.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-150x114.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-768x586.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-500x382.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/7-800x610.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center is-style-default\">Brad Pitt.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"769\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2367\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8.jpg 769w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-231x300.jpg 231w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-115x150.jpg 115w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/8-500x650.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 769px) 100vw, 769px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Jon Snow and the White King, the show ended badly.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"689\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2368\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9.jpg 689w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-207x300.jpg 207w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-103x150.jpg 103w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/9-500x726.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 689px) 100vw, 689px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Liam Nesson.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2369\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-300x182.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-150x91.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-768x467.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-500x304.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/10-800x486.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Leonardo Di Caprio.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"566\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2370\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-300x170.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-150x85.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-768x435.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-500x283.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/11-800x453.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Peter Dinklage.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"675\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2371\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12.jpg 675w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-203x300.jpg 203w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-101x150.jpg 101w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/12-500x741.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 675px) 100vw, 675px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Matt Damon.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"664\" height=\"10