-768x899.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-500x585.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/15-800x937.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Someone close.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"976\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2375\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-300x293.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-150x146.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-768x750.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-500x488.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/16-800x781.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Fish hair.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"648\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2376\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-300x194.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-150x97.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-768x498.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-500x324.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/17-800x518.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elephant family.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"702\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/18.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2377\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/18.jpg 1000w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/18-300x211.jpg 300w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/18-150x105.jpg 150w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/18-768x539.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/18-500x351.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/18-800x562.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">College friend.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"904\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/19.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2378\" srcset=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/19.jpg 904w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/19-271x300.jpg 271w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/19-136x150.jpg 136w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/19-768x850.jpg 768w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/19-500x553.jpg 500w, https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/19-800x885.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 904px) 100vw, 904px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Tom Cruise.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"864\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://thearticular.github.io/articular/wp-content/uploads/20.jpg\" 